  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lumiel the Awakening is an Open World Top Down Adventure RPG Game. The game features a Fantasy Sci-fi Setting, revolving around an island where our hero is stranded. The game places a strong emphasis on exploration, building, and harvesting. As players venture away from towns, villages, settlements, and roads, they will engage in battles against hordes of monsters. Collecting rare artifacts, resources, and equipment will be crucial to continuously enhance the player's strength. Numerous dungeons, secrets, and hidden treasures await discovery throughout the game world.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lumiel the Awakening is an Open World Top Down Adventure RPG Game. The game features a Fantasy Sci-fi Setting, revolving around an island where our hero is stranded. The game places a strong emphasis on exploration, building, and harvesting. As players venture away from towns, villages, settlements, and roads, they will engage in battles against hordes of monsters. Collecting rare artifacts, resources, and equipment will be crucial to continuously enhance the player's strength. Numerous dungeons, secrets, and hidden treasures await discovery throughout the game world.</p>",
